Supervise and Train Agents on Service Cloud Voice

Train Your Agents on Service Cloud Voice
Use these resources to help your agents become familiar with Voiceâ€™s softphone and features.

Listen In to a Voice Call
Supervisors can listen in to any ongoing call from Omni Supervisor, but the customer isn't notified. The agent is notified in the chat transcript.

Interrupt a Voice Call with Supervisor Barge-In
Barge in and take over the call quickly to respond to an agent flag or deescalate an ongoing voice call.

Change Agents or Groups Assigned to Voice Queues
Reassign agents to different queues if their role changes or they switch teams. How you reassign depends on your telephony provider.

Change Agents Assigned to Groups
Reassign agents from one queue to another when Queue Management is enabled.

Analyze Call Recordings for Insights
Einstein Conversation Insights identifies key moments in conversation recordings, providing insight into call structure and agent performance.

View Real-Time Metrics about Your Amazon Connect Contact Center
Open the Real-Time Metrics dashboard directly from Omni Supervisor to view key metrics such as agents online and calls handled.

Track Contact Center KPIs with the CRM Analytics App
Supervisors can track key performance indicators like call volume, average handle time, and more. Customize how contact center data is displayed.
title: Supervising and Training Agents on Service Cloud Voice
